name: Taijie Printing in China
overview:
Taijie (Shenzhen) Printing CO. Ltd is professional Printing Company in China, located in Shenzhen, China. We have more than 10 years experiences in Packaging Printing in China; Our factory plant covers 3600 square meters and fixed asset is 18 million RMB, the factory was founded in Jan 5, 1990 and put into operation in Feb28 , 1990 and we provide best service , with the development we introduced advanced equipments and technology , the business scope is also widened from design before printing ,professional printing to further process and our advantageous printing products including children books printing, packaging boxes printing, calendars, mock-up cards, etc., We’ve becoming one of the largest and most professional printing and packing group on large scale in China and operate internationally.
